{"tid":514024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"先達買iPhone6s發脹　內地男要求更換被打傷","createTime":"2017-12-30T06:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T08:32:56.000Z","uid":62599,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"495fcfbd8500a70f4a9b530a8f03951cd925756a","tid":514024,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=tq1kDz1fn1a4gO7PTbgixJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=736b6a3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】旺角發生傷人案件，一名內地男子，早前在亞皆老街先達廣場購買一部iPhone 6手機，使用一直沒問題。<br />\n<br />\n約3個月前，他打算買一部iPhone 6s給女兒使用，於是到同一間店舖購買，但該店缺貨，於是到商場另一間店購買，但使用後不久，電池即發脹，更頂爆屏幕。<br />\n<br />\n今日上午11時許，他拿着手機到店舖要求更換，但店員不同意，雙方發生爭執，期間內地男被人揮拳打傷右眼，於是報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護員到場將他送院治理，警方初步調查後，將一名店員拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20171230/20171230131724lc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fhknews%2F20171230%2F20171230131724lc.html&d=tq1kDz1fn1a4gO7PTbgixJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=649b2bbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/hknews/20171230/20171230131724lc.html</a>"},{"pid":"4366d9fe8da42d4c088c50802f304362a36c5d98","tid":514024,"uid":60092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"先達狗vs大陸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aa9b61ac9eb64322a0cc6b6884034922f201ed","tid":514024,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"先達狗打得好 坐返個零月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc6ea863b44c5b2086c1332944366c4f17f1856","tid":514024,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"美帝iphone分裂中港同胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}